Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.62,0:24:17.49,Dragon Ball 3,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ven, fantasía{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.49,0:24:20.13,Dragon Ball 2,,0,0,0,, {\i1}Suki sa misuteri{\i0}
